
Mostly GPL and MIT type Licences. All source code licences are open source licenses

Qt is free for open source projects can be used for Linux/Android/Windows developent 
but requires registraion and license aggreement. 
Qt is used for GUI on all operatiing system and is required to build No Limit Connect
Qt is available at https://www.qt.io/download (The open source use version is at bottom of web page)

Visual Studio 2019 Community Edition can be used for No Limit Connect windows developement
and is free but requires registraion and license aggreement.  


All other tools used to build No Limit Connect DO NOT require registraion.

